prompts.frontCover: A vibrant watercolor illustration for a greeting card front. In a humorous and playful scene, cartoon versions of the couple from the reference photo are depicted. Lao Lao, wearing her light blue sweatshirt and glasses, is gleefully sitting atop Jordan's shoulders. Jordan, in his tan hoodie, has a comically strained but happy expression as he holds her up. Lao Lao triumphantly holds two large, delicious-looking boba milk teas high in the air, one in each hand, like trophies. Playful splashes of watercolor in pastel shades of pink, yellow, and blue surround them like confetti. The background is a clean, simple white wash, allowing the characters and the boba to be the main focus. Centered below the illustration, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, dark teal handwritten cursive script. The entire image has soft edges, blended colors, and a lighthearted, joyful feel, capturing a funny, exaggerated moment. Flat 2D artwork style.
